com.here.mobility.sdk.map.route

Class Route.Maneuver

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.mobility.sdk.map.route.Route.Maneuver
  • Enclosing class:
    Route

    public abstract static class Route.Maneuver
extends Object
    Represents a maneuver to make while travelling. "Maneuvers" are actions such as turning, merging, exiting a roundabout, etc.
